 UI&#39;, SimHei, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; z-index: 0; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); box-sizing: border-box; width: 720px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">推动教学、医疗改革、促进信息化新技术、新装备的深入应用，</span></p><p class=\"article-content\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 10px auto; outline: none; border: 0px; font-family: Helvetica, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, SimHei, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; z-index: 0; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); box-sizing: border-box; width: 720px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">秀才思量：艺术教育（美术宝）小有所成，“智慧教育”，望有所建树！</span></p><p class=\"article-content\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 10px auto; outline: none; border: 0px; font-family: Helvetica, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, SimHei, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; z-index: 0; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); box-sizing: border-box; width: 720px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">正襟曰“沿承二十载美国基因，凝聚多年技术积淀，参与此会，我之幸也！”</span></p><p class=\"article-content\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 10px auto; outline: none; border: 0px; font-family: Helvetica, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, SimHei, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; z-index: 0; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); box-sizing: border-box; width: 720px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"article-img\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170526/1495786567633575.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"692\" height=\"554\" title=\"\"/><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, SimHei, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></p><p