a Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%;  font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em;  font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170901/1504264586803123.jpg\" title=\"1504264586803123.jpg\" alt=\"1504264586803123.jpg\" width=\"692\" height=\"519\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em;  font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%;  font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em;  font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%;  font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%;  font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">当虹科技核心产品的技术优势采用了“GPU+UPU”的组合架构，与&nbsp;NVIDIA&nbsp;的合作，大并发的编转码处理能力更大程度上提升了编转码效率，使得编转码效率可以达到传统编转码器的五到十倍。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em;  font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%;  font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em;  font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em;  font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170901/1504264594366593.jpg\" title=\"1504264594366593.jpg\" alt=\"1504264594366593.jpg\" width=\"692\" height=\"519\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">全球最大的电子公司之一的&nbsp;PHILIPS&nbsp;携手当虹科技，展示了从制作端到播放端的HDR 一体化解决方案，该方案可以实现智能色调管理技术把数百万小时的SDR 内容（包括直播和现在的片源库）换为HDR，再次印证了当虹科技致力于为人们提供最佳的视听体验的愿景。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em;  font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170901/1504264605913001.jpg\" title=\"1504264605913001.jpg\" alt=\"1504264605913001.jpg\" width=\"692\" height=\"519\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em;  font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em;  font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%;  font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">在展台现场，4K HDR 视频节目素材均来自华语地区最大的4K内容生产分发平台&nbsp;4K花园，当虹科技所提供的 4K HDR直播编转码以及视频云服务，全面支撑了前期拍摄到后期DIT支持，内容分发的一整套4K解决方案。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em;  font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em;  font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em;  font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170901/1504264615790132.jpg\" title=\"1504264615790132.jpg\" alt=\"1504264615790132.jpg\" width=\"692\" height=\"519\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em;  font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em;  font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em;  font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%;  font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">当虹科技在现场所提供的“全场景直播解决方案、融合媒体内容生产平台、融合媒体播控与运营平台及行业应用解决方案”，想客户所想，急用户所急，真正解决了台内、新媒体及行业客户的实际痛点，得到了大家的一致认可。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em;  font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%;  font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%;  font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">未来，当虹科技将一如既往地坚持与全球合作伙伴的良好合作，携手为人们提供最佳的视听体验。</span></p><p><br/></p>','BIRTV2017 , 您的支持，我们携手共赢！','1503504000','59a911645e3d3.png','null','null','null');
INSERT INTO `ldhkj_article` VALUES ('268','134','25','<p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">这是一个直播的时代，这是一个轻松互动的时代，当虹科技的直导播一体化产品，帮助您实现轻松直播、欢乐互动的最佳“利器”。BIRTV 展会现场，当虹科技所展示的直导播一体化产品，便捷的操作流程与丰富的产品功能，重塑了客户对直导播一体机的认知。</span></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170901/1504264731176404.jpg\" title=\"1504264731176404.jpg\" alt=\"1504264731176404.jpg\" width=\"692\" height=\"358\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">Arcvideo Director 直导播一体机，是基于直播流信号接入切换分发的一体化导播产品，结合 当虹科技 23 年的音视频技术积累和视频云平台运营经验，运用多格式现场信号接入、远程手机推流、直播信号云调度、多机位切换、信号录制、信号监视、图文叠加、调音、效果变换、导播输出等技术处理，为报社、广电新媒体、在线教育、互联网视频、政府企业等提供现场直导播服务。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;font-size: medium; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170901/1504264736165110.jpg\" title=\"1504264736165110.jpg\" alt=\"1504264736165110.jpg\" width=\"692\" height=\"268\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">采用军工产品设计标准，最大限度保障设备的运行稳定性，完美适应各种复杂的直导播环境；独有的私有协议，加上当虹云中心化调度，优化的直连调度算法和智能 CDN 调度机制来降低网络延时，延时低至 600毫秒 之内。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170901/1504264751883229.jpg\" title=\"1504264751883229.jpg\" alt=\"1504264751883229.jpg\" width=\"692\" height=\"387\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;  font-size: medium; white-space: normal; text-align: justify;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">利用延时、垫片、切换等机制来保障直播安全，直播延时时间最大可至 300秒，并支持 FTB 瞬间紧急直切；支持 SDI 内嵌数字音频、小蜜蜂、麦克风等多种音频输入，支持对音频音量增益、声道均衡、声道复制、混音、音频独奏及跟随等操作。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;  font-size: medium; white-space: normal; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;  font-size: medium; white-space: normal; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170901/1504264763161590.jpg\" title=\"1504264763161590.jpg\" alt=\"1504264763161590.jpg\" width=\"692\" height=\"416\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">通过低延时、双向互动的导播调度、现场连麦功能，让原本孤立的演播室和多路现场之间建立稳定连接，实现演播现场和远程观众、导播和现场记者之间的实时交流；通过当虹云平台，既实现了手机推流的接入，也实现了直导播输出流的一站式云发布，达到线上线下的联动。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;  font-size: medium; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170901/1504264770979347.jpg\" title=\"1504264770979347.jpg\" alt=\"1504264770979347.jpg\" width=\"692\" height=\"555\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;  font-size: medium; white-space: normal; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;  font-size: medium; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">直导播一体机内置了当虹科技独有的全自主知识产权编转码算法，更加稳定可控，具备低带宽高画质特性，并可实现 OTA （Over-the-Air Technology）无缝升级到H.265，为运营商节省带宽资源，降低运营成本，提升用户视觉感受。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;  font-size: medium; white-space: normal; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;  font-size: medium; white-space: normal; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170901/1504264781935984.jpg\" title=\"1504264781935984.jpg\" alt=\"1504264781935984.jpg\" width=\"692\" height=\"519\"/></span></p><p><br/></p>','当虹科技：直导播一体化产品， 重塑您的认知','1503676800','59a90fdae1c40.png','null','null','null');
INSERT INTO `ldhkj_article` VALUES ('270','225','26','<p><span style=\"color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(227, 227, 227);\">【流媒体网】消息：作为广电传媒领域规模最大，影响力最广的行业盛会，北京国际广播电影电视设备展览会(BIRTV2017)于8月23--26日如期而至。当虹科技将在北京中国国际展览中心3号馆3005展位，呈现精心打造的多款智能视音频产品与解决方案，并携手全球顶级的合作伙伴，为您深度解读“融合媒体、智慧广电”。</span></p>','BIRTV2017开幕在即 当虹科技展会亮点抢先看','1503475193','59a913a8ba79c.png','http://dvb.lmtw.com/zhengce/201708/148111.html?from=timeline&isappinstalled=0#10006-weixin-1-52626-6b3bffd01fdde4900130bc5a2751b6d1','null','null');
INSERT INTO `ldhkj_article` VALUES ('271','225','26','<p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">当虹科技所提供的“线上+线下” 融合媒体内容生产平台，不仅可以满足台内业务，更可以针对新媒体的内容生产，提供便捷高效的一体化解决方案与云服务；同时推出的融合媒体播控与运营平台为台网互动与增值运营提供了多种可能；而现场展示的静态人脸识别智能媒资人脸检索系统，基于当虹科技独有的ICR智能内容识别引擎，可以全面应用与音像资料智能媒检索与备播节目敏感人物筛查。</span></p>','【BIRTV2017】每日聚焦/8月23日','1503417600','59a9174225da5.png','https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MzcyNjM0NQ==&mid=2650539951&idx=1&sn=b7f18785b2bd428a6ba9d2a9d2645dc0&chksm=be9a0d4989ed845fb36d1c83eb5c3edbd3ac35f3046bf4beb6c761231c5fa99f76b2bfae7d53&mpshare=1&scene=1&srcid=0823GDNaMstLJXOUEhagSrgl#rd','null','null');
INSERT INTO `ldhkj_article` VALUES ('272','225','26','<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">8月23日至26日，第二十六届北京国际广播电影电视展览会（简称BIRTV2017）在北京中国国际展览中心举办，作为广电行业知名企业，当虹科技携带旗下全媒体产品线盛装参展。大会期间，当虹科技高级产品总监孙波先生接受了DVBCN记者的采访，重点讲解了当虹科技全场景直播解决方案。</span></p>','【专访】当虹科技如何成为“直播平台”的最佳搭档','1503590400','59a915dff13a3.png','http://www.dvbcn.com/2017/08/25-146160.html','null','null');
INSERT INTO `ldhkj_article` VALUES ('273','225','26','<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 微软雅黑, SimHei, SimSun; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">作为全球领先的智能视频解决方案与视频云服务提供商，杭州当虹科技有限公司（简称当虹科技）和全球信息产业的领导者英特尔紧密合作，提出了基于英特尔® 至强® 可扩展平台的 Arcvideo HDR 转码解决方案。全面升级 换代的至强® 可扩展平台，可为计算、网络和存储带来针对工作负载优化的性能，向下 一代云基础设施提供坚实基础，并赋能数据分析、人工智能、高性能计算、网络转型 等各类应用。当虹科技利用至强® 可扩展平台可提高计算密集型工作负 载性英特尔® AVX-512（英特尔® 高级矢量拓展指令集 512）的新特性，能高效地将 SDR 和 HDR 格式进行转换，并对 HDR 视频进行高效编码，打造了从内容生产到内容 加工、转换到内容播放的 4K/HDR 视频处理解决方案</span></p>','当虹科技HDR 转码解决方案携手英特尔® 至强® 可扩展平台 助力广播级视频行业升级换代','1503676800','59a91649b1212.png','http://bc.tech-ex.com/manufacturer/2017/86506.html?from=timeline&isappinstalled=0','null','null');
