alt=\"1492049528890696.jpg\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170413/1492049528890696.jpg\" width=\"290\" height=\"177\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 2em;\"><br/></p></li><li><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\"><strong>视频内容运营商节目输出</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">面向专业的视频内容提供商，为其节目内容生产平台，提供<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">高效、<span style=\" font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 22px;\">智能化的内容制作/拆条生产服务</span>，</span>既减少人力投入，又提高生产效率。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\"></span><img title=\"1492049533177740.jpg\" alt=\"1492049533177740.jpg\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170413/1492049533177740.jpg\" width=\"290\" height=\"163\"/></p></li></ol><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><br/></p>','null','1495209600');
