 line-height: 2em;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170515/1494853832351920.png\" title=\"1494853832351920.png\" alt=\"1494853832351920.png\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 2em;\"><br/></p></li><li><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"><strong>视频监控降码率收录</strong></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">面向视频监控领域，需要对大量监控数据存档以便以后查看，为其平台提供高密度、低码率、易调度、多协议的直播信号收录服务。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 2em;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170515/1494853838925359.png\" title=\"1494853838925359.png\" alt=\"1494853838925359.png\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\"/></p><p><br/></p></li></ol>','null','1495382400');
